{
  "texts": [
    "To address this discrepancy, we designed an algorithm based on clinical knowledge to harmonize MS-DRG codes across different time points to a unified version-specifically, MS-DRG version 34.0 8.",
    "The process include:",
    "Standardize use of abbreviations and capitalization within DRGs.",
    "For example, we replaced all \"W/O\" to \"WITHOUT\", \"CATH\" to \"CATHETERIZATION\" and \"PROC\" to \"PROCE-DURES\". 2.",
    "Using a fuzzy string match algorithm (TheFuzz: https:// github.com/seatgeek/thefuzz) to find those DRGs not matching to any MS-DRG v.34 codes."
  ]
}